      <Description>Initial release</Description>
      <Author>Dominic Colella</Author>
    </CalDefChangeRecord>
    <CalDefChangeRecord>
      <Version>2</Version>
      <Date>31OCT2014</Date>
      <Description>Added REQUESTING_STREAM_NATIVE_HFM_WB in response to Harman Assembla ticket #1223.  Re-Ordered Streams based on Harman Assembla ticket #1265.</Description>
      <Author>Dominic Colella</Author>
    </CalDefChangeRecord>
    <CalDefChangeRecord>
      <Version>3</Version>
      <Date>12/18/2015</Date>
      <Description>Adjusted priorities of streams STREAM_BLUETOOTH_SCO, STREAM_NATIVE_ATCP_RING, STREAM_NATIVE_DTCP_CALL, STREAM_NATIVE_DTCP_PROMPT, STREAM_NATIVE_DTCP_RING, STREAM_NATIVE_HFM, STREAM_NATIVE_HFM_WB, STREAM_NATIVE_MUTEX_PROMPT, STREAM_NATIVE_PHN_VR, STREAM_NATIVE_RING, STREAM_NATIVE_SPEECH, STREAM_RING, and STREAM_VOICE_CALL to handle various OnStar Application audio issues.</Description>
      <Author>Dominic Colella</Author>
    </CalDefChangeRecord>
    <CalDefChangeRecord>
      <Version>4</Version>
      <Date>5/31/2016</Date>
      <Description>Changed stream interaction default value between DTCP_ECALL and DTCP_ECALL to GRANT_CHANGE due to MY17 integration issues.</Description>
      <Author>Dominic Colella</Author>
    </CalDefChangeRecord>
    <CalDefChangeRecord>
      <Version>5</Version>
      <Date>6/15/2017</Date>
      <Description>Updated the usage field for this calibration to support the new &quot;Global A/B&quot; categorization in the CalDef tool.</Description>
      <Author>Ginnard Kimbrough</Author>
    </CalDefChangeRecord>
    <CalDefChangeRecord>
      <Version>6</Version>
      <Date>10/2/2017</Date>
      <Description>Updated vehicle architectural usage to add GEM usage for this calibration because it fell within the current criteria of calibrations that require GEM usage, which are any calibrations that would be used for Low Radio Global B application.</Description>
      <Author>Ginnard Kimbrough</Author>
    </CalDefChangeRecord>
    <CalDefChangeRecord>
      <Version>7</Version>
      <Date>9/11/2018</Date>
      <Description> CR1261915 - Added new stream type STREAM_NATIVE_PROJ_ALT_AUDIO </Description>
